<div class="comment" id="comment9460">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20101119082810/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/959/" target="_top">uehaj</a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20101119082810/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/9460/">#9460</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2009/08/08 19:57 GMT"));</script><noscript>2009/08/08 19:57 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20101119082810/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/groovy/">
	  Groovy
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;
<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <p>Groovyではloanパターンは標準ライブラリでサポートされてますので，利用側の例として一つ。</p>

	</div>
	
	<p class="link">
	  参考: <a href="/web/20101119082810/http://groovy.codehaus.org/groovy-jdk/java/net/Socket.html#withStreams%28groovy.lang.Closure%20closure%29">Socket#withStreams</a>
	</p>  
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>new Socket(&quot;www.google.com&quot;, 80).withStreams { ins, outs -&gt;
  outs.write(&quot;GET / HTTP/1.0\n\n&quot;.getBytes())
  ins.eachLine {
    println it
  }
}
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
